Package: text2numR
Type: Package
Title: Text to Number Encoding and Decoding Tools
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
  person("Hasindu", "Koshitha", email = "koshithahasindu@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides functions to encode lowercase alphabetic text into numeric
    positions (a = 1, ..., z = 26) and decode numeric sequences back into text.
    Useful for educational purposes, cryptographic exploration, and string manipulation.
